import React from 'react'
import { Container, Row, Col} from 'react-bootstrap'

const Footer = () => {
    return (
       
            <footer>
                 <Container>
              <Row>
                  <Col className ='text-center py3'>
                      Copyright © myshop
                  </Col>
              </Row>
              </Container>
            </footer>
    )
}

export default Footer
